{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/600.gif?t=1619088916\" /><br>Ancient Abyss is a 2D Zelda-like action game where you will explore mysterious and hidden events in a randomly generated maze. As you progress, you\u2019ll gain more power and collect items to help you reach further into the maze. As you walk through the layers of the maze and reach the bottom of the abyss, you\u2019ll discover mysterious and dark forces, tucked away, so no one would find them...<br><br>Ancient Abyss features the thrilling battle and perma-death mechanics of the Roguelike genre, as well as the exploration and discovery of 2D Zelda games.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/\u653e\u706b\u6218\u6597.2020-09-28_15_59_42.gif?t=1619088916\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features:</strong></h2><strong>\u2022 RogueZelda: </strong>An action game that combines RogueLike and 2D Zelda elements, allowing players to experience exploration and discovery in a randomly generated maze. The game combines the depth of a RogueLike game with a thrilling perma-death experience. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/\u7ffb\u6eda\u51fb\u843d\u6c34.gif?t=1619088916\" /><br><br><strong>\u2022 Explore: </strong>The game is full of unreachable and hidden areas, but players have the opportunity to master new skills and acquire new items at any time in the game. These new abilities will help players explore further to discover treasures and secrets hidden within the maze. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/\u98df\u7269\u5546\u5e97.2020-09-28_16_19_41.gif?t=1619088916\" /><br><br><strong>\u2022 Stimulating Combat: </strong>A wide selection of melee and ranged weaponry allow for multiple styles of pla